{"tid":1429896,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"不要說濫權，試著說犯法","createTime":"2019-08-07T15:13:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T19:04:24.000Z","uid":276716,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c8dfe849cc2e8c1f5a647c0173dc0ce5d4e64079","tid":1429896,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:13:33.000Z","msg":"承接上個post,文宣要注意字眼<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1386793/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1386793/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n小弟再講一個字眼，好重要，就係<span style=\"color: red;\">濫權</span>vs<span style=\"color: red;\">犯法</span>。<br />\n<br />\n濫權係先承認對方有權，不過用得過火啫。咁過幾多先算犯法呢，係完全由對方演繹，係和稀泥，任佢spin。<br />\n<br />\n假設警察打咗市民十拳，而你形容為濫權，咁是否打九拳就不屬於濫權呢？咁如果打一百拳到市民死咗，是否仍然只係濫權呢？畢竟打一百拳同十拳都係數量分別啫。<br />\n<br />\n可見濫權完全係on 9，犯法就係犯法，斬釘截鐵，必須受法律制裁。<br />\n<br />\n由今日起唔好再講濫權！"},{"pid":"cca9eda46f23cf76e1a9f9a23f255a99170bb871","tid":1429896,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:17:06.000Z","msg":"講注意字眼"},{"pid":"d73b85139fe5d5f5a5bb71ff6eb1bedd1191062f","tid":1429896,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cca9eda46f23cf76e1a9f9a23f255a99170bb871","tid":1429896,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:17:06.000Z","msg":"講注意字眼"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:23:18.000Z","msg":"注意字眼"},{"pid":"223abd54f368ff37bda5669cf8401ea1fe2679a1","tid":1429896,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:35:13.000Z","msg":"注意字眼"},{"pid":"5257e93cb3044bfbaa4c02f152b1bacd83b2311f","tid":1429896,"uid":168703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:40:17.000Z","msg":"黎到夏慤道呀，帶乜撚野好呀？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1429895\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1429895</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"894260972b9406864ef85afe616daf9e7d1205e1","tid":1429896,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"